## Next Steps
To start collecting Speed Insights data:
1. Ensure the project is deployed to Vercel
2. Enable Speed Insights in your Vercel project dashboard
3. Data will begin collecting after users visit your deployed site
4. Access insights through the Vercel dashboard's Speed Insights section

